PathnamesPage.title: Pathnames
PathnamesPage.description:
The pathnames are internationalized too.

If you're using the default language English, you'll see /en/pathnames in the browser address bar on this page.

If you change the locale to German, the URL is localized accordingly (/de/pfadnamen).

Site.title: namiPOS
Site.description: namiPOS is a point of sale system that is designed to be used by small to medium businesses. It is a web-based application that can be accessed from any device with a web browser. It is designed to be simple and easy to use, while still providing all the features that a business needs to manage their sales and inventory.
